nodes.text: Dolan was a Human male who lived in the underworld of Coruscant during the Clone Wars. After the war ended, he didn't believe that the Jedi betrayed the Republic and went on to join Jedi Master Fy-Tor-Ana and The Eleven. In order to protect the resistance, Dolan spied on the Galactic Empire and helped Solace to hide a group of refugees. However, he was killed by Inquisitor Malorum who been hired to hunt down resistance leaders and traitors.
